Description:
Our partner is a global provider of software development services and IT outsourcing, under the Part-Time Employment Program for final-year students, is looking for a Trainee Data Engineer in its office in Budapest. You’ll be part of a team of professionals who are ready to find the best tailor-made IT solutions for their multinational clients in various industries and solve complex problems.
Feladatok
Collaborate with the team to implement new features to support the growing data needs;
Build and maintain pipelines to extract, transform, and load data from a wide variety of data sources;

